  "body": "/kind bug\r\n\r\n**What happened**:\r\nUsing `YAMLToJSONDecoder` subsequent reads after `io.ErrShortBuffer` would return values from the next yaml section, rather than the rest of the section being read.\r\n\r\n**What you expected to happen**:\r\n\r\nI'd expect the rest of the current section to get returned until the whole section has been read\r\n\r\n**How to reproduce it (as minimally and precisely as possible)**:\r\n\r\nSee tests here: https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/pull/58817/files#diff-3b3ea800b8ebe625d0defd76c2e6f827R57\r\n\r\n\r\n**Anything else we need to know?**:\r\n\r\nPR to fix: https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/pull/58817",
